        public void finish()
        Description copied from interface: Transaction
        Commits or marks this transaction for rollback, depending on whether Transaction.success() or Transaction.failure() has been previously invoked. All ResourceIterables that where returned from operations executed inside this transaction will be automatically closed by this method.
